apter_1:_A_Tight_Squeeze\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Chapter 1: A Tight Squeeze</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> as the topic of a VHS tape, conjecturally known as the \"</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://poppy-playtime.fandom.com/wiki/Final_Log\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Final Log</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">.\" He made his first physical appearance in </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://poppy-playtime.fandom.com/wiki/Chapter_2:_Fly_in_a_Web\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Chapter 2: Fly in a Web</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>.</em> He is also featured in </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://poppy-playtime.fandom.com/wiki/Chapter_3:_Deep_Sleep\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Chapter 3: Deep Sleep</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> and </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://poppy-playtime.fandom.com/wiki/Chapter_4:_Safe_Haven\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Chapter 4: Safe Haven</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">. He appears in </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://poppy-playtime.fandom.com/wiki/Chapter_5:_Broken_Things\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Chapter 5: Broken Things</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> as its main antagonist. The </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://poppy-playtime.fandom.com/wiki/Monster_Narrator\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">voice</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> that directs </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://poppy-playtime.fandom.com/wiki/Huggy_Wuggy\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\